<Layout title="Marketing Automation for Lead Generation + Conversion Optimisation">



  <ContainerFW>
    <SectionEmail>
      <Fragment slot="title">
        Marketing automation for lead gen + conversion optimisation.
      </Fragment>
      <Fragment slot="desc">
        We apply the same cutting-edge AI / Automations within your marketing 
        that the best performing global brands are using. Helping reduce manual hours 
        across your business, completely customised to your needs. Only available to <a href="/moonshot">Moonshot Plan</a> customers.
      </Fragment>
      <Fragment slot="cover">
        <Picture
                  src={PagecoverHero}
                  sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 2000px, 1000px"
                  widths={[1000, 1500, 2000]}
                  aspectRatio="3:2"
                  background="#f2f2f2"
                  fit="cover"
                  position="center"
                  class="w-full rounded duration-200 hover:shadow-sm"
                />
      </Fragment>
    </SectionEmail>

  </ContainerFW>

  <ContainerXL>
    <SectionHeadImg>
      <Fragment slot="title">
        Performance-focused code.
      </Fragment>
      <Fragment slot="desc">
        Velocity is one of the most powerful and versatile website frameworks available. Version 7 built on the best of Web3 languages, AstroJS (in our humble opinion).
        Completely accessible, seo-friendly code. Pre-integrated with the necessities, without losing any pageload performance.
        Visually stunning, TailwindCSS styling, with codelinting and postcss preconfigured. 50+ user-friendly components worth of truly beautiful code.
        Completely owned by your business with a lifetime license, so you don't need to worry about subscription traps again.
      </Fragment>
      <Fragment slot="cover">
        <Picture
                  src={Pagecover}
                  sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 2000px, 1000px"
                  widths={[1000, 1500, 2000]}
                  aspectRatio="3:2"
                  background="#f2f2f2"
                  fit="cover"
                  position="center"
                  class="w-full rounded duration-200 hover:shadow-sm"
                />
      </Fragment>
    </SectionHeadImg>
  </ContainerXL>

  <ContainerXL>
    <SectionHeadSecImg>
      <Fragment slot="title">
        Conversion-focused design.
      </Fragment>
      <Fragment slot="desc">
        Velocity's conversion-focused component and layout design optimizes user-flow for your business with ease. 
        Quickly building web pages for your business that showcase a beautiful user journey to sales and conversions.
      </Fragment>
      <Fragment slot="cover">
        <Picture
                  src={PagecoverSecondary}
                  sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 2000px, 1000px"
                  widths={[1000, 1500, 2000]}
                  aspectRatio="3:2"
                  background="#f2f2f2"
                  fit="cover"
                  position="center"
                  class="w-full rounded duration-200 hover:shadow-sm"
                />
      </Fragment>
    </SectionHeadSecImg>
  </ContainerXL>

  <ContainerXL>
    <SectionTextarea>
      <Fragment slot="title">Rock-solid integrations.</Fragment>
      <Fragment slot="desc">
        Velocity7 is writen in AstroJS and ready to be extended endlessly. But we've taken the liberty of
        pre-integrating, in the most perfomant way, the best web technologies we know of. All of our secrets, 
        with a helping hand from our team and some good laughs along the way.
      </Fragment>
      <Fragment slot="cover">
        <Picture
                  src={CoverTextarea}
                  sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 2000px, 1000px"
                  widths={[1000, 1500, 2000]}
                  aspectRatio="3:2"
                  background="#f2f2f2"
                  fit="cover"
                  position="center"
                  class="w-full rounded duration-200 hover:shadow-sm"
                />
      </Fragment>
      <Fragment slot="iconleft">
        <Icon class="w-16 h-16" name="simple-icons:zapier" />
      </Fragment>
      <Fragment slot="titleleft">
        Zapier API
      </Fragment>
      <Fragment slot="textleft">
        Zapier's powerful automation platform works directly
        with Velocity7. Automate tasks, synchronize data, 
        and reduce costs. All made simple with Velocity7 
        API connection.
      </Fragment>
      <Fragment slot="iconright">
        <Icon class="w-16 h-16" name="simple-icons:netlify" />
      </Fragment>
      <Fragment slot="titleright">
        Netlify DNS & CDN
      </Fragment>
      <Fragment slot="textright">
        All our Velocity sites are powered by Netlify's powerful, 
        load-balancing network of servers to deliver your content 
        to the end user faster than anyone else. Absolutely necessary
        with the cell networks available in Australia. Take back control 
        of your website's velocity with the speed of Velocity7 on Netlify's network.
      </Fragment>
      <Fragment slot="iconleft2">
        <Icon class="w-16 h-16" name="simple-icons:googleads" />
      </Fragment>
      <Fragment slot="titleleft2">
        GTM Conversion Tracking
      </Fragment>
      <Fragment slot="textleft2">
        Maximize your advertising effectiveness with Google Ads' 
        conversion tracking built deeply into Velocity7. Easily 
        track and measure conversions that matter most to your 
        business. Gain valuable insights into customer behavior 
        and optimize your ad strategy accordingly. With Google Ads' 
        comprehensive conversion tracking, you can make data-driven 
        decisions and drive higher ROI for your advertising efforts.
      </Fragment>
      <Fragment slot="iconright2">
        <Icon class="w-16 h-16" name="simple-icons:stripe" />
      </Fragment>
      <Fragment slot="titleright2">
        Stripe Payments
      </Fragment>
      <Fragment slot="textright2">
        Streamline your payment process and boost sales with Stripe's 
        secure payment gateway. With one-click checkout, you can 
        provide a seamless payment experience for your customers, 
        reducing cart abandonment and driving conversions. Benefit 
        from Stripe's transparent pricing, and robust fraud prevention 
        from day one for your business. For frictionless payment experiences.
      </Fragment>      
    </SectionTextarea>
  </ContainerXL>

  <Container>

    <Sectionhead>
      <Fragment slot="title">Turn Around in 21 Days.</Fragment>
      <Fragment slot="desc"
        >We get straight to work when you're ready, just order below. I'll come directly to your businesses anywhere in South East Queensland 
        before any designs are started, to see your current position and learn your future goals. From here, a 21 day turn around will be 
        accomplished with a 97% success rate. While still giving you the option for 2 free full revisions at any point, keeping you kept in the 
        creative loop as frequently as you'd like.
      </Fragment>
    </Sectionhead>

