      <Fragment slot="title">Ready to Launch?</Fragment>
      <Fragment slot="desc" class="max-w-4xl">
        Move your business to Velocity7 with Aidxn Design and start crushing it with ease in your industry. Leave the world of churn web design.
      </Fragment>
    </Sectionhead>
